{"tid":2202363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《最緊要有事》葵涌荔景紀律部隊宿舍二座印傭確診","createTime":"2020-09-14T13:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:36:07.000Z","uid":242262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94fda7d561d044624c782c840913740d134dd549","tid":2202363,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"留名集氣等睇紀律部隊男戶主快d確診<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名於荔景紀律部隊宿舍第2座居住的41歲女印傭（第4947號個案）。據了解，荔景紀律部隊宿舍第2座有不同紀律部隊同住。確診女傭平日多往美孚新邨街市，周日放假也多留在家中。她與僱主於9月10日同往荔景社區會堂接受全民檢測後，證實確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/GCN2ELSSVBCNTISQX4HJMZRN54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FGCN2ELSSVBCNTISQX4HJMZRN54%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=46cec5dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FGCN2ELSSVBCNTISQX4HJMZRN54%2F&h=847a3bb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/GCN2ELSSVBCNTISQX4HJMZRN54/</a>"}]}